Enum CoreRouter.Connectivity

    CoreRouter

    public static enum CoreRouter.Connectivity
extends java.lang.Enum<CoreRouter.Connectivity>
    The possible types of connectivity for route calculation

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      DEFAULT
      Default connectivity, whether route will be calculated online or offline is determined by the HERE SDK based on each routing type, whether the HERE SDK is allowed to access network, whether traffic is enabled, whether this is enough map data, and other factors.
      OFFLINE
      Attempts offline routing regardless whether there is enough map data on the device.
      ONLINE
      Attempts online routing regardless whether device is online or whether the HERE SDK is allowed to access network.

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • DEFAULT

        public static final CoreRouter.Connectivity DEFAULT
        Default connectivity, whether route will be calculated online or offline is determined by the HERE SDK based on each routing type, whether the HERE SDK is allowed to access network, whether traffic is enabled, whether this is enough map data, and other factors.

      • OFFLINE

        public static final CoreRouter.Connectivity OFFLINE
        Attempts offline routing regardless whether there is enough map data on the device. If there is not enough map data the request might fail. If it fails, it will not try online.

      • ONLINE

        public static final CoreRouter.Connectivity ONLINE
        Attempts online routing regardless whether device is online or whether the HERE SDK is allowed to access network. If the device is offline, the request will fail. If it fails, it will not try offline.
